# PRIMARY conflict fix: per-PR changelog FRAGMENTS in changelog.d/ (one unique
# file per PR → PRs can't collide on the log; see changelog.d/README.md). Feature
# PRs no longer edit CHANGELOG.md directly. This union driver is kept as
# belt-and-suspenders: GitHub's auto-merge ignores .gitattributes merge drivers,
# so union only helps LOCAL merges (the collected CHANGELOG.md + any stray direct
# edit). Safe ONLY because the file is append-only (entries are never edited in
# place); do NOT extend union to in-place-edited files (STATUS.md is excluded).
CHANGELOG.md merge=union
